{"about_the_game":"Shelley Manor is a combination of reality and fantasy, where the time seems to have stopped before entering the manor walls. You will meet known enemies, all of whom come from classical works, and some allies. <br><br>Control Alex, a tourist that ended up there after being tricked by the townsfolk. Explore the hallways and rooms and help them escape before it\u2019s too late.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999270/extras/AlexManor.png?t=1720612245\" /><br><br>The player must run, push and throw to reach its goal by completing the various riddles the manor is covered with. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999270/extras/puzzlegif.gif?t=1720612245\" /><br><br>With fixed cameras and dynamic puzzles, escaping seems harder with every passing time; encountering enemies every step of the way might make Alex lose hope, but fear not! They\u2019re not alone in this tale.<br><br>A friendly NPC will help guide them with different dialogues and save points along several rooms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999270/extras/HighresScreenshot00000.png?t=1720612245\" /><br><br>Hide through the levels, distract enemies and interact with the level scenery to solve the different puzzles in front of you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999270/extras/GifZombie.gif?t=1720612245\" /><br><br>Shelley Manor is a linear free exploration game where the player can choose how to use their time.<br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player game<br></li><li>5 Unique enemies<br></li><li>Three different zones<br></li><li>Rich and immersive environment </li></ul><br>Start your adventure through the manor and find your way out before it\u2019s too late.","achievements":{"h